{"tid":2299730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［原片報導］Pompeo 未有與拜登任命的「國務卿」對話，會展開程序睇GSA決定，並跟據法律行事。","createTime":"2020-11-25T04:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:56:57.000Z","uid":270220,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e673bbe3a7f638b79546ec0d7bf0a670d7eaf6","tid":2299730,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"記者問有冇同Tony Blinken （拜登想揀嘅「國務卿」）講話。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>Pompeo 答未有。今日會展開個程序，會睇GSA決定，同時做任何事都會跟據法律。我哋會做到（we will make this work)。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n英文原文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2xWfpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2xWfpr.jpg&h=10f9df74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/acyn/status/1331378108130201601?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Facyn%2Fstatus%2F1331378108130201601%3Fs%3D21&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=1dd21725\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Facyn%2Fstatus%2F1331378108130201601%3Fs%3D21&h=fcddaa48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/acyn/status/1331378108130201601?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n成條片，3:50後開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D9QEkgoEShY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD9QEkgoEShY&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKAOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=b547b156\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D9QEkgoEShY</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n比較原文，睇下傳媒點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧稱國務院已開始交接程序<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299515</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，在美國總務署表示正式啟動過渡流程之後，國務院亦已經開始交接程序，蓬佩奧在霍士新聞表示，會按法律的要求，展開交接工作。蓬佩奧表示，他仍未與拜登的國務卿人選布林肯接觸，但他對此表示期待。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>首先Pompeo 就冇講「對此表示期待」。至於「會按法律的要求，展開交接工作」，自己睇原文思考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nWe will make this work.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/mouse2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14236a54579ad47f74c9dc0ee17ab1fc882bc470","tid":2299730,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"報道*"},{"pid":"19f326ed4b39e3875ce1e27a8801f03f95cc1cb2","tid":2299730,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig3_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d27f826fb95a9e67d7537eb9dfc3e77d4354190","tid":2299730,"uid":166308,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"個個都加鹽加醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/angry_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d35918d4eb11b2fb76ab5b145ce79a9339aff8","tid":2299730,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aa20927db0e0128b4d8549a0f5259153758b67","tid":2299730,"uid":358445,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\nfake news真係好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94446fc2b2eb133770a75fa7ca926ad808cfe876","tid":2299730,"uid":99243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202